description: A distinguished 2023 construction 3 bed 2 bath penthouse residence in a prime East side South Boston location with 2 parking! Meticulously decorated with an expansive open floor plan and a chef’s kitchen featuring Metropolitan cabinetry, gold hardware, large island, integrated appliances and Calacatta Venetian quartz counters. The dining area and custom dry bar open to the private deck with a gas grill. A stunning custom built-in is a focal point of the living area perfectly suited for entertaining. The king-sized primary bedroom has a spa-like bath, walk in closet and room for additional furnishings. Two additional bedrooms offer options for multipurpose use. Notable features include upgraded custom light fixtures, window treatments, recessed lights and in-unit laundry. Professionally managed, pet-friendly elevator building with bike and stroller storage. A+ location steps to Castle Island, M Street Beach/Park, Broadway restaurants/shops, the Edison project and the Seaport District.
